this service has a notable safety, operational and equipment standards issues, some ferries are better than others, or worse depending upon your perspective. delays are commonplace due to loading and unloading issues and services may be cancelled or postponed during periods of inclement weather. it may be prudent to avoid sea crossings during the monsoonal period when sea conditions may lead to deteriorated comfort levels or a dangerous crossing. see the gili islands and lombok articles for full details concerning travelling and arriving in lombok and it's nearby islands. cruise ships occasionally stop so that passengers can tour or shop. 